author: cbegin
msg: Reimplemented XML support to always use DOM.  String XML params/results are no longer handled separately, but instead they are converted at input and output.  This ensures more consistency in the implementation and reduces redundant code.  There may be some performance penalties for String based XML, however these can be tuned later (or the user could simply use DOM).
